value.value: Adult intrinsic neuron with ipsilateral arbors in multiple VNC neuromeres (Takemura et al., 2023; Marin et al., 2024). It is a secondary neuron of the 06B hemilineage (Takemura et al., 2023; Marin et al., 2024). It receives input in the T1 leg neuropil and T2 leg neuropil and sends output to the T2 leg neuropil and T3 leg neuropil (Takemura et al., 2023; Marin et al., 2024). Its predicted neurotransmitter is gaba (Eckstein et al., 2024). There are approximately 2 of these cells per organism and their somas are found in the mesothoracic neuromere (Takemura et al., 2023; Marin et al., 2024).
